The [documentation for importing from Trac|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Importing+Data+from+Trac] mentions a mapping of users, as shown below:
{quote}
Regardless of whether you specify mapping, JIRA will automatically create usernames for missing users.
{quote}

However, this mapping is never explained further. It seems important to specify: What this mapping does, where it is set and how it works. 

This sentence seems to indicate that users from Trac can be mapped to users in JIRA, but this is never explained or detailed.
